column1:
Why are a buncha dudes ridin' the Ferris wheel
together?

I certainly don't mind—look how beautiful the
view is at night.
I think I'm going to cry...

Hahaha, same here. I can't see anythin' through
my tears...

Sure, fine—but why'd you invite US!?
You should've asked one of them!

I'm supposed to be soaking up this romantic
view with Lady Ann...

Is a Ferris wheel an unsuitable location for
"guy time"?

I mean, there's no laws about it, buuut it is a
real blow to a guy's ego.

Riding a Ferris wheel can pain a man? The heart
sounds incredibly complicated.

Dude, wouldn'tcha rather do this with someone
you're... you know, "into"!?

Now's not the time for such frivolous matters.
We have a case to solve.

And I already know who I'm destined to be
with, unlike a whining child like you, Ryuji.
I wonder when I'll meet my soulmate...

Well, whatever! You guys better tell me if any
o' you get a girlfriend!

Although, maybe not findin' out right away
isn't the worst thing—I mean, I'd be happy
for ya, but also kinda lonely, too...
Why!? I thought we were best buds!
Oh, no way! Don't tell me you already...!?

The heart of a man... Yet another mystery has
been added to the list.
Lady Ann... I wish you were here!

We enjoyed the Sapporo
evening view together...
